<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>Meet the Team — Floryn Garden</title>
<meta name="description" content="Meet the passionate people behind Floryn Garden — the team crafting every bouquet with love and delivering every arrangement with a smile."/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300;1,400;1,600&family=Jost:wght@200;300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<style>
/* ── TOKENS (same palette as landing) ── */
:root{
  --ink:#18191A; --forest:#243B2E; --moss:#3A5C47; --sage:#7A9E87;
  --cream:#E8DEC8; --parch:#DECDAF; --blush:#C9A090; --petal:#E0C2B0;
  --rose:#B85C42; --gold:#A87830; --glt:#C89848; --white:#EDE5D0;
  --light-border:rgba(26,26,26,.09); --r:16px;
  --s1:8px; --s2:16px; --s3:24px; --s4:32px; --s5:40px; --s6:48px;
  --s7:56px; --s8:64px; --s9:72px; --s10:80px; --s12:96px; --s14:112px;
  --text-xs:.7rem; --text-sm:.8125rem; --text-base:.9375rem;
  --text-lg:1.125rem; --text-xl:1.375rem; --text-2xl:1.875rem;
}
*,*::before,*::after{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth;font-size:16px;scrollbar-width:none;}
html::-webkit-scrollbar{display:none;}
body{background:var(--white);color:var(--ink);font-family:'Jost',sans-serif;font-weight:400;overflow-x:hidden;line-height:1.6;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;}
img{display:block;max-width:100%;}
a{text-decoration:none;cursor:pointer;}

/* ── CURSOR ── */
#cd,#cr{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;border-radius:50%;pointer-events:none;z-index:9999;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);will-change:transform;}
#cd{width:6px;height:6px;background:var(--forest);transition:background .2s;}
#cr{width:38px;height:38px;border:1.5px solid var(--forest);transition:width .22s,height .22s,border-color .22s;}
body.ch #cr{width:56px;height:56px;border-color:var(--rose);}
body.ch #cd{background:var(--rose);}

/* ── NAV ── */
nav{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:200;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:0 var(--s12);height:80px;background:rgba(36,59,46,.97);backdrop-filter:blur(24px);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.07);transition:height .3s;}
.nav-logo{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:1.75rem;font-weight:300;letter-spacing:.3em;color:var(--white);}
.nav-logo em{font-style:normal;color:var(--glt);}
.nav-links{display:flex;gap:var(--s5);align-items:center;}
.nav-right{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:var(--s2);}
.nav-toggle{
  display:none;
  width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:14px;
  border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.18);
  background:rgba(255,255,255,.05);
  color:rgba(253,250,244,.9);
  cursor:pointer;
}
.nav-toggle svg{width:18px;height:18px;stroke:currentColor;fill:none;stroke-width:2;}
.nav-links a{font-size:var(--text-xs);letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(253,250,244,.62);transition:color .25s;font-weight:400;}
.nav-links a:hover,.nav-links a.active{color:rgba(253,250,244,.95);}
.nav-cta{background:var(--rose);color:var(--white)!important;padding:11px 28px;border-radius:100px;font-size:var(--text-xs)!important;letter-spacing:.16em;box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(184,92,66,.35);transition:background .25s,transform .25s,box-shadow .25s!important;}
.nav-cta:hover{background:var(--gold)!important;transform:translateY(-2px)!important;}

/* ── PAGE HERO ── */
.page-hero{padding-top:160px;padding-bottom:var(--s12);padding-left:var(--s12);padding-right:var(--s12);background:linear-gradient(152deg,#0e1812 0%,#1c3025 45%,#132418 100%);position:relative;overflow:hidden;}
.page-hero-glow{position:absolute;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(ellipse 55% 75% at 74% 26%,rgba(184,92,66,.18) 0%,transparent 55%);}
.page-hero-inner{position:relative;z-index:2;max-width:600px;}
.page-eyebrow{font-size:var(--text-xs);letter-spacing:.34em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--rose);margin-bottom:var(--s2);font-weight:500;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;}
.page-eyebrow::before{content:'';width:24px;height:1px;background:var(--rose);}
.page-h1{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:clamp(3rem,5.5vw,5rem);font-weight:300;line-height:1.05;color:var(--white);margin-bottom:var(--s3);letter-spacing:-.01em;}
.page-h1 em{font-style:italic;color:var(--petal);}
.page-sub{font-size:var(--text-base);font-weight:300;color:rgba(253,250,244,.55);max-width:420px;line-height:1.85;}

/* ── BREADCRUMB ── */
.breadcrumb{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:var(--s4);}
.breadcrumb a,.breadcrumb span{font-size:var(--text-xs);letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(253,250,244,.38);}
.breadcrumb a:hover{color:var(--petal);}
.breadcrumb .sep{color:rgba(253,250,244,.2);}
.breadcrumb .cur{color:var(--petal);}

/* ── SECTION COMMONS ── */
.sec{padding:var(--s14) var(--s12);}
.eyebrow{font-size:var(--text-xs);letter-spacing:.34em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--rose);margin-bottom:var(--s2);font-weight:500;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;}
.eyebrow::before{content:'';width:24px;height:1px;background:var(--rose);}
.sec-h2{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:clamp(2.6rem,4.5vw,4.4rem);font-weight:300;line-height:1.06;letter-spacing:-.01em;}
.sec-h2 em{font-style:italic;color:var(--forest);}

/* ── TEAM SECTION ── */
.team-bg{background:var(--parch);}
.team-intro{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;align-items:end;margin-bottom:var(--s9);}
.team-tagline{font-size:var(--text-base);font-weight:400;line-height:1.85;color:rgba(26,26,26,.62);text-align:right;max-width:320px;margin-left:auto;}
.team-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:var(--s3);}
.tmc{position:relative;}
.tm-photo{position:relative;border-radius:var(--r);overflow:hidden;aspect-ratio:3/4;background:var(--cream);margin-bottom:var(--s3);border:1px solid var(--light-border);}
.tm-img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block;transition:transform .5s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1);}
.tmc:hover .tm-img{transform:scale(1.05);}
.tm-placeholder{position:absolute;inset:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:14px;background:linear-gradient(145deg,var(--cream),var(--parch));}
.pl-icon{width:88px;height:88px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(36,59,46,.09);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;}
.pl-icon svg{width:40px;height:40px;stroke:var(--forest);fill:none;stroke-width:1.2;}
.pl-label{font-size:var(--text-xs);letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(26,26,26,.38);font-weight:400;}
.tm-badge{position:absolute;top:var(--s2);left:var(--s2);background:rgba(253,250,244,.92);backdrop-filter:blur(8px);border-radius:100px;padding:6px 16px;font-size:var(--text-xs);letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--forest);font-weight:500;}
.tm-ov{position:absolute;inset:0;border-radius:var(--r);background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(36,59,46,.9) 0%,transparent 52%);opacity:0;transition:opacity .32s;display:flex;align-items:flex-end;padding:var(--s3);}
.tmc:hover .tm-ov{opacity:1;}
.tm-soc{display:flex;gap:var(--s1);}
.tsb{width:32px;height:32px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.32);border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:var(--white);transition:background .25s,border-color .25s;}
.tsb svg{width:13px;height:13px;stroke:currentColor;fill:none;stroke-width:2;}
.tsb:hover{background:var(--rose);border-color:var(--rose);}
.tm-name{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:var(--text-2xl);font-weight:400;color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:6px;line-height:1.3;}
.tm-role{font-size:var(--text-xs);letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--sage);font-weight:500;margin-bottom:var(--s2);}
.tm-bio{font-size:var(--text-base);font-weight:400;line-height:1.78;color:rgba(26,26,26,.62);}

/* ── VALUES SECTION ── */
.values-bg{background:var(--cream);}
.values-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:var(--s4);margin-top:var(--s8);}
.val-card{background:var(--white);border-radius:var(--r);padding:var(--s5);border:1px solid var(--light-border);transition:transform .32s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1),box-shadow .32s,border-color .32s;}
.val-card:hover{transform:translateY(-8px);box-shadow:0 24px 56px rgba(26,26,26,.09);border-color:rgba(184,92,66,.18);}
.val-icon{width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:var(--s3);}
.val-icon svg{width:24px;height:24px;stroke-width:1.5;fill:none;}
.ic-rose{background:rgba(184,92,66,.09);} .ic-rose svg{stroke:var(--rose);}
.ic-green{background:rgba(36,59,46,.07);} .ic-green svg{stroke:var(--forest);}
.ic-gold{background:rgba(168,120,48,.09);} .ic-gold svg{stroke:var(--gold);}
.val-title{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:var(--text-xl);font-weight:400;color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:10px;}
.val-body{font-size:var(--text-sm);font-weight:300;color:rgba(26,26,26,.54);line-height:1.75;}

/* ── CTA STRIP ── */
.cta-strip{background:var(--forest);padding:var(--s10) var(--s12);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:var(--s6);}
.cta-strip-text .ey{font-size:var(--text-xs);letter-spacing:.3em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--petal);margin-bottom:var(--s2);}
.cta-strip-text h2{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:clamp(2rem,3.5vw,3rem);font-weight:300;color:var(--white);line-height:1.1;}
.cta-strip-text h2 em{font-style:italic;color:var(--petal);}
.cta-strip-btns{display:flex;gap:var(--s2);flex-shrink:0;}
.btn-fill{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;background:var(--rose);color:var(--white);padding:16px 42px;border-radius:100px;font-size:var(--text-xs);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;box-shadow:0 12px 32px rgba(184,92,66,.38);transition:background .25s,transform .25s;}
.btn-fill:hover{background:var(--gold);transform:translateY(-3px);}
.btn-ghost{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.2);color:rgba(253,250,244,.68);padding:16px 32px;border-radius:100px;font-size:var(--text-xs);letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;transition:border-color .25s,color .25s;}
.btn-ghost:hover{border-color:rgba(255,255,255,.5);color:var(--white);}

/* ── FOOTER ── */
footer{background:var(--ink);color:var(--cream);padding:var(--s12) var(--s12) var(--s6);}
.ftop{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.6fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:var(--s8);padding-bottom:var(--s8);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.07);}
.flogo{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:1.85rem;font-weight:300;letter-spacing:.26em;color:var(--white);margin-bottom:var(--s2);display:block;}
.flogo em{font-style:normal;color:var(--rose);}
.fdesc{font-size:var(--text-sm);font-weight:300;color:rgba(245,239,224,.36);line-height:1.85;max-width:260px;margin-bottom:var(--s4);}
.fsoc{display:flex;gap:10px;}
.fsb-wrap{width:36px;height:36px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;transition:border-color .25s;}
.fsb-wrap:hover{border-color:var(--rose);}
.fsb-wrap svg{width:14px;height:14px;stroke:rgba(245,239,224,.38);fill:none;stroke-width:2;transition:stroke .25s;}
.fsb-wrap:hover svg{stroke:var(--rose);}
.fcol-title{font-size:.7rem;letter-spacing:.26em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--glt);margin-bottom:var(--s3);font-weight:400;}
.fcol ul{list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:var(--s2);}
.fcol ul a{font-size:var(--text-sm);font-weight:300;color:rgba(245,239,224,.36);transition:color .25s;}
.fcol ul a:hover{color:var(--cream);}
.fbot{padding-top:var(--s4);display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;}
.fcopy{font-size:.7rem;font-weight:300;color:rgba(245,239,224,.2);}
.fcopy em{font-style:normal;color:var(--rose);}
.flove{font-size:.7rem;color:rgba(245,239,224,.2);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;}
.flove svg{width:12px;height:12px;fill:var(--rose);stroke:none;}

/* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
@media(max-width:1100px){.team-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);}.values-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);}}
@media(max-width:900px){
  nav{padding:0 var(--s4);}
  .page-hero,.sec{padding:var(--s10) var(--s4);}
  .page-hero{padding-top:140px;}
  .team-intro{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:var(--s4);}.team-tagline{text-align:left;margin-left:0;}
  .cta-strip{flex-direction:column;text-align:center;padding:var(--s8) var(--s4);}.cta-strip-btns{justify-content:center;}
  .ftop{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:var(--s6);}
}
@media(max-width:600px){
  nav{padding:0 var(--s3);}
  .nav-toggle{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;}
  .nav-links{
    display:none;position:absolute;top:80px;left:0;right:0;
    padding:16px var(--s3);
    flex-direction:column;gap:var(--s2);
    background:rgba(36,59,46,.98);
    backdrop-filter:blur(24px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(24px);
    border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.07);
  }
  #nav.nav-open .nav-links{display:flex;}
  .page-hero{padding:120px var(--s3) var(--s8);}
  .sec{padding:var(--s9) var(--s3);}
  .team-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;}
  .values-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
  .cta-strip-btns{flex-direction:column;align-items:center;}
  .ftop{grid-template-columns:1fr;}.fbot{flex-direction:column;gap:var(--s2);}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div id="cd"></div>
<div id="cr"></div>

{# ── NAV ── #}
<nav id="nav">
  <a href="{{ path('app_home') }}" class="nav-logo">FLORYN<em>.</em></a>
  <div class="nav-right">
    <button id="nav-toggle" class="nav-toggle" type="button" aria-label="Toggle navigation" aria-expanded="false">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><line x1="4" y1="7" x2="20" y2="7"/><line x1="4" y1="12" x2="20" y2="12"/><line x1="4" y1="17" x2="20" y2="17"/></svg>
    </button>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="{{ path('app_home') }}">Home</a>
      <a href="{{ path('app_about') }}" class="active">About Us</a>
      <a href="{{ path('app_contact') }}">Contact</a>
      <a href="{{ path('app_login') }}" class="nav-cta">Order Now</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

{# ── PAGE HERO ── #}
<div class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-hero-glow"></div>
  <div class="page-hero-inner">
    <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="breadcrumb">
      <a href="{{ path('app_home') }}">Home</a>
      <span class="sep">·</span>
      <span class="cur">About Us</span>
    </nav>
    <div class="page-eyebrow">The Faces Behind Floryn</div>
    <h1 class="page-h1">Meet our <em>team</em></h1>
    <p class="page-sub">The passionate people who pour their hearts into every bouquet — crafting beauty and making every reservation a joy, one bloom at a time.</p>
  </div>
</div>

{# ── TEAM GRID ── #}
<section class="sec team-bg" id="team">
  <div class="team-intro">
    <div>
      <div class="eyebrow">The People</div>
      <h2 class="sec-h2">Who we <em>are</em></h2>
    </div>
    <p class="team-tagline">A dedicated crew of florists, developers, and dreamers working together to make Floryn an experience worth remembering.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="team-grid">
    {% set team = [
      {name: 'HIRAI MOMO', role: 'Project Lead & Developer', badge: 'Team Lead', photo: 'images/team/team-1.jpg', bio: 'Oversees the whole Floryn system and ensures every customer experience is seamless from browse to reservation.'},
      {name: 'CHOU TYUZU', role: 'UI Designer & Developer', badge: 'Designer', photo: 'images/team/team-2.jpg', bio: 'Designs every page of the Floryn shop to feel as beautiful and inviting as the flowers themselves.'},
      {name: 'SANA MINATOZAKI', role: 'Backend Developer', badge: 'Developer', photo: 'images/team/team-3.jpg', bio: 'Powers the ordering, inventory, and reservation tracking that keep Floryn running smoothly every day.'},
      {name: 'PARK JIHYO', role: 'QA & Customer Experience', badge: 'QA', photo: 'images/team/team-4.jpg', bio: 'Makes sure every page, order, and feature works perfectly so customers always leave happy.'}
    ] %}
    {% for member in team %}
    <div class="tmc">
      <div class="tm-photo">
        {% if member.photo is defined and member.photo %}
          <img src="{{ asset(member.photo) }}" alt="{{ member.name }}" class="tm-img" loading="lazy">
        {% else %}
          <div class="tm-placeholder">
            <div class="pl-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H8a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/><circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/></svg></div>
            <span class="pl-label">Photo coming soon</span>
          </div>
        {% endif %}
        <span class="tm-badge">{{ member.badge }}</span>
        <div class="tm-ov">
          <div class="tm-soc">
            <a href="#" class="tsb"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 19c-5 1.5-5-2.5-7-3m14 6v-3.87a3.37 3.37 0 00-.94-2.61c3.14-.35 6.44-1.54 6.44-7A5.44 5.44 0 0020 4.77 5.07 5.07 0 0019.91 1S18.73.65 16 2.48a13.38 13.38 0 00-7 0C6.27.65 5.09 1 5.09 1A5.07 5.07 0 005 4.77a5.44 5.44 0 00-1.5 3.78c0 5.42 3.3 6.61 6.44 7A3.37 3.37 0 009 18.13V22"/></svg></a>
            <a href="#" class="tsb"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M16 8a6 6 0 016 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 00-2-2 2 2 0 00-2 2v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 016-6z"/><rect x="2" y="9" width="4" height="12"/><circle cx="4" cy="4" r="2"/></svg></a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="tm-name">{{ member.name }}</div>
      <div class="tm-role">{{ member.role }}</div>
      <p class="tm-bio">{{ member.bio }}</p>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

{# ── OUR VALUES ── #}
<section class="sec values-bg" id="values">
  <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:var(--s2);">
    <div class="eyebrow" style="justify-content:center;">What We Stand For</div>
    <h2 class="sec-h2" style="text-align:center;">Our <em>values</em></h2>
    <p style="font-size:var(--text-base);font-weight:300;color:rgba(26,26,26,.52);max-width:440px;margin:var(--s2) auto 0;line-height:1.82;">The principles that guide every stem we arrange and every delivery we make.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="values-grid">
    <div class="val-card">
      <div class="val-icon ic-rose"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 22s-8-4.5-8-11.8A8 8 0 0112 2a8 8 0 018 8.2c0 7.3-8 11.8-8 11.8z"/><path d="M12 13a3 3 0 100-6 3 3 0 000 6z"/></svg></div>
      <div class="val-title">Freshness First</div>
      <p class="val-body">We source directly from local farms every morning. If it isn't fresh, it doesn't leave our shop. Period.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="val-card">
      <div class="val-icon ic-green"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg></div>
      <div class="val-title">Excellence in Craft</div>
      <p class="val-body">Every arrangement is made by hand with intention — each petal and ribbon placed with care and artistry.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="val-card">
      <div class="val-icon ic-gold"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H5a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 00-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 010 7.75"/></svg></div>
      <div class="val-title">Customer Joy</div>
      <p class="val-body">We measure success not in transactions, but in the smiles our bouquets bring to the people who receive them.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ── CTA STRIP ── #}
<div class="cta-strip">
  <div class="cta-strip-text">
    <div class="ey">Ready to experience Floryn?</div>
    <h2>Send someone <em>flowers today</em></h2>
  </div>
  <div class="cta-strip-btns">
    <a href="{{ path('app_login') }}" class="btn-fill">Shop Now</a>
    <a href="{{ path('app_contact') }}" class="btn-ghost">Contact Us</a>
  </div>
</div>

